         8 building pieces
         24 evidence tokens
         Detective piece
         Surveillance token



&mdash;description from the publisher

This new combined eHASL rulebook contains the rules for all the HASL modules and mini-modules produced to date. When additional HASL modules are released, the rules will be added to this product.

Errata has been incorporated into the rules. Non-rules errata (e.g., for map sheets) and Q&A have been compiled at the end. Updated editions will be published when new HASLs are produced.

eHASL includes:


     Chapter O (RED FACTORIES);
     Chapter P (KAMPFGRUPPE PEIPER I and II);
     Chapter Q (PEGASUS BRIDGE);
     Chapter R (A BRIDGE TOO FAR);
     Chapter T (BLOOD REEF: TARAWA);
     Chapter V (VALOR OF THE GUARDS);
     Chapter FB (FESTUNG BUDAPEST);
     Chapter DN (DINANT);
     Chapter HF (HATTEN IN FLAMES); 
     Chapter SF (SWORD AND FIRE: MANILA);
     Chapter SM (DROP ZONE: STE-M&Egrave;RE-&Eacute;GLISE);
     Chapter SaP (SLAUGHTER AT PONYRI);
     Chapter Z (KAKAZU RIDGE, EDSON&rsquo;S RIDGE, RILEY&rsquo;S ROAD, PRIMOSOLE BRIDGE, SINGLING, SUICIDE CREEK, SAND AND BLOOD, SWEDISH VOLUNTEERS, SPARROW FORCE, plus HELL&rsquo;S CORNER)


Note: The eHASL rulebook does not contain any scenarios, maps, or counters for the above HASL chapters.

&mdash;description from the publisher

Sarah Elizabeth Jacobs is known by most as a wife, a member of the local gardening club, an avid patron of the Valley Falls Library, the organist for the First Presbyterian Church of Valley Falls, and a volunteer at the local animal shelter. Because she has so much to live for, it comes as a great shock to everyone who knows her when she is found hanging at the end of a rope in her garage. Even more shocking is the letter pinned to her chest that says simply:
&ldquo;Thou shalt not suffer a witch to live. This one is but the first I have identified as in league with the devil. I will expose the others and any who aid them in the coming days.&rdquo;
The note is signed simply, &ldquo;Witchfinder.&rdquo;
With the promise of more deaths, you must work quickly to identify the Witchfinder and put a stop to this Witch Hunt&hellip;before it&rsquo;s too late. But, move carefully and with great caution as it&rsquo;s now the Season of the Witch!

&mdash;description from the publisher

Something lurks behind the veil&hellip; something dark, something hungry&hellip;

Your mastery of the sandwich arts has summoned the Hungry Ones from beyond the great kitchen door at the edge of the universe (you know, the squeaky one). Now, they are here - and, in return for the finest bready morsels you can muster, they will grant you a boon&hellip;

Dare you join the Secret Order?

