New biomes and enemies have been revealed in the deepest caves of Hoxes IV. Shoot, mine, rock and stone your way through the following new biomes:


     Hollow Bough, Hoxes IV strangest biological oddity, this biome appears to be the inside of a massive hollow tree, invested eith vines.



     Crystaline Caverns, one of the most beautiful sights on Hoxes IV, unfortunately the silicate crystals are basically worthless.



     Sandblasted Corridors, one of Hoxes IV driest regions, dominated by windblasted tunnels that will send you flying if you arent carefull.



     Dense Biozone, A subterranean rainforest, full of writhing carnivorous plant life. Be careful miners.


But beware, these new biomes also bring new threats, including the following enemies:


     Dreadnaught Twins (Arbalest & Lacerator);
     Septic Spreader;
     Huuli Hoarder;
     Nayaka Thrawler;
     Barage Infestor.


And some new enemies never seen before:

     Pod Spawner;
     Mist Sprayer.

Up to 8 guests are given an answer card and they are asked to answer 26 rhyming couplets that act as a clue to a word.
First to come up with a correct answer to all 26 clues wins. If no-one answers all 26 then the winner will be the the one with the most correct answers.
Example:
He freed old England from the Danes;
But with his cooking took no pains;
Answer: Alfred
